observations.reason:
The non-collection of the remaining balance of delinquent accounts was attributed to the following:
-Demand letters were  “Returned to Sender” due to reasons such as: incorrect or incomplete address;
-Notice of Cancellation of Assessment remained active in the database. No updated name of property owner;
-Mother lot already subdivided but remained active in the database;
-Real  property owners claimed tax exemption;  Jarco Realty, GSIS, Beneco, BWD, and NHA;
-Duplicate Assessment; and
-Donated property to the City Government remained private and taxable.
Audit Team will continuously monitor the actions undertaken by management to resolve the issue.
